x;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"50\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">17</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5168%; height: 358.297px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"213\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Importance of having a specific and dedicated standing committee for the purpose of reviewing the Health and Education policies or can it be assigned to one of the existing committees.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 23.6572%; height: 358.297px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"190\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">-Implications of National Medical Service as Autonomous entity(Medical Staffs working in Administration and HR Section)</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">-Implications of relocating Taba Dental Hospital from JDWNRH.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">-Making the newly established Committee a standing committee.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.2377%; height: 358.297px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"155\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">-* For the appointment of the new Committee\'s Chairperson and members, a meeting will be held among the Chairperson of the other nine Committees</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8182%; height: 358.297px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"83\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">-Chairperson of Committees</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 9.61885%; height: 358.297px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"77\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 409.797px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 6.23925%; height: 409.797px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"50\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">18</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5168%; height: 409.797px;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"213\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Legislative Committee to take up review of laws, rules &amp; regulations, and policies which are not in harmony with each other. (Refer- Law Review report by OAG)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 23.6572%; height: 409.797px;\" valign=\"top\" width